before redrawing.
</para></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</para></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><emphasis role="bold">Return value:</emphasis></term>
<listitem><para>
<variablelist>
<varlistentry><term>0</term>
<listitem><para>Redrawing was successful.
</para></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term>1</term>
